ussystem f\u00fcr Schorndorf. mobilit\u00e4t \u2013 9. Wissenschaftsforum 2017,Mobility and Digital Transformation \u2013 Challenges and Future Paths, Duisburg,2017.<span class=\"Occurrences\"><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceGS\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"google-scholar-link gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"Google Scholar\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Kl%C3%B6tzke%2C%20M.%2C%20Brost%2C%20M.%2C%20Fraedrich%2C%20E.-M.%2C%20Gebhardt%2C%20L.%2C%20Karnahl%2C%20K.%2C%20Kopp%2C%20G.%2CK%C3%B6nig%2C%20A.%2C%20M%C3%BCller%2C%20A.%2C%20Sippel%2C%20T.%2C%20Ulmer%2C%20F.%3A%20BOOLEAN%20%E2%80%93%20Ein%20haltestellenlosesQuartiersbussystem%20f%C3%BCr%20Schorndorf.%20mobilit%C3%A4t%20%E2%80%93%209.%20Wissenschaftsforum%202017%2CMobility%20and%20Digital%20Transformation%20%E2%80%93%20Challenges%20and%20Future%20Paths%2C%20Duisburg%2C2017.\"><span><span>Google Scholar</span></span></a></span></span></div></li><li class=\"Citation\"><div class=\"CitationNumber\">[18]</div><div class=\"CitationContent\" id=\"CR18\">Ludwig, J. N.: Absicherung eines neuartigen Interieur-Ma\u00dfkonzeptes f\u00fcr einFahrzeug des \u00d6PNV. Bachelorarbeit Hochschule Esslingen, Fakult\u00e4tFahrzeugtechnik, 2017, unver\u00f6ffentlicht.<span class=\"Occurrences\"><span class=\"Occurrence OccurrenceGS\"><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"google-scholar-link gtm-reference\" data-reference-type=\"Google Scholar\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Ludwig%2C%20J.%20N.%3A%20Absicherung%20eines%20neuartigen%20Interieur-Ma%C3%9Fkonzeptes%20f%C3%BCr%20einFahrzeug%20des%20%C3%96PNV.%20Bachelorarbeit%20Hochschule%20Esslingen%2C%20Fakult%C3%A4tFahrzeugtechnik%2C%202017%2C%20unver%C3%B6ffentlicht.\"><span><span>Google Scholar</span></span></a></span></span></div></li></ol></div></section><section class=\"Section1 RenderAsSection1\"><h2 class=\"Heading\" id=\"copyrightInformation\">Copyright information</h2><div class=\"ArticleCopyright content\"><div cla